_sText:
So here's another quick gun game one. I haven't played it yet, but it should turn out ok. Plenty lighter than my past couple maps with neat little features here and there. I didn't see a reason for a 3D skybox on this one, but enjoy!

BEWARE: Falling will kill you!

v1 UPDATE: Ok, so the odd textures have been removed, 3d skybox added, and I fixed ambient sound in the canyon. There you go! Thanks for suggestions! (Oh and the screenshots show the new one.)

v2 UPDATE: Alrighty, spawn points should check out ok, now.
